sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Reviewer
    participant UI as Dashboard UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as MongoDB

    R->>UI: Access Dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /reviewer/dashboard/stats
    API->>DB: Query assignments
    DB-->>API: Return data
    API-->>UI: Statistics
    UI-->>R: Display Overview

    R->>UI: Click "Start Review"
    UI->>API: POST /assignments/{id}/start
    API->>DB: Update status to "in_progress"
    DB-->>API: Confirm update
    API-->>UI: Success response
    UI-->>R: Show Review Form

    R->>UI: Fill Review Form
    R->>UI: Click "Submit Review"
    UI->>API: POST /assignments/{id}/submit
    API->>DB: Save review data
    API->>DB: Update status to "completed"
    DB-->>API: Confirm save
    API-->>UI: Success response
    UI-->>R: Show confirmation
